                    "(method) TSNode:id()",
                    "  -\u003e string",
                    "```",
                    "",
                    "---",
                    "",
                    " Get a unique identifier for the node inside its own tree.",
                    "",
                    " No guarantees are made about this identifier's internal representation,",
